'''Pri-Andylan Propulsion Systems''' was a major corporation located on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Duro/Legends|Duro]]. They specialized in the production of [[Repulsorlift/Legends|repulsorlifts]] and other propulsion systems. Their strength was such that they owned several orbital [[Shipyard/Legends|shipyards]] including a major ship-producing platform above Duro. The company prospered under the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Empire]] and maintained several expensive contracts under this government. After the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]], the Empire ended almost all their contracts with Pri-Andylan, and the company suffered, eventually being purchased by the [[Corporate Sector Authority/Legends|Corporate Sector Authority]].<ref name="University">{{GamerCite|2|The University of Sanbra Guide to Intelligent Life: The Duros}}</ref>

